'''飓风安娜'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Anna}}）是1961年对[[中美洲|中美洲]]和[[向风群岛|向风群岛]]构成影响的一场大型飓风，也是[[1961年大西洋飓风季|1961年大西洋飓风季]]形成的首场获得命名的风暴和首场飓风。系统于7月20日经位于向风群岛上空[[热带辐合带|热带辐合带]]内部的[[东风波|东风波]]发展而成，成为热带风暴后向西穿越[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]。由于外界环境有利，安娜于7月20日晚达到飓风强度。次日清晨，风暴又有增强，风速达到现代[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]的二级飓风标准。气旋系统深化，于7月21日晚达到三级飓风强度，成为[[热带气旋等级|大型飓风]]{{#tag:ref|大型飓风是指[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]达到三级或以上的飓风<ref>{{cite book | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/A3.html | chapter = What is a super-typhoon? What is a major hurricane? What is an intense hurricane? | editor = Goldenberg, Stan | edition = 4.8 | title = Frequently Asked Questions | first = Chris | last = Landsea | publisher = Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | accessdate = 2016-04-10 | date = 2015-06-01 | location = Miami, Florida | type = FAQ | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304040802/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/A3.html | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>|group="注"}}。7月22日达到最高强度后，安娜在掠过[[洪都拉斯|洪都拉斯]]北海岸期间略有弱化。风暴继续减弱，于7月24日以风力时速130公里强度[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]][[伯利兹|英属洪都拉斯]]（如今叫“伯利兹”）。气旋在陆地上空迅速弱化，于当天晚上消散。

成为热带气旋并在背风群岛上空发展期间，安娜给[[格林纳达|格林纳达]]带去狂风，不过当地只有少数农作物、树木和电线杆受损。另外多个岛屿出现强烈阵风，但没有因此遭受破坏。行经[[委内瑞拉|委内瑞拉]]以北洋面时，风暴在该国产生强风，最高风速达到每小时115公里。洪都拉斯北部因狂风受到大面积破坏，该国有至少36户民居被毁，另有228户受损。[[格拉西亚斯-阿迪奥斯省|格拉西亚斯-阿迪奥斯省]]受到气旋重创，数以百计的居民无家可归，另外还有约5000棵椰子树被强风推倒。整场飓风一共造成1人死亡，经济损失约为30万美元（1961年[[美元|美元]]）{{#tag:ref|如无特别说明，所有损失数额均为1961年[[美元|美元]]价值。|group="注"}}，其中大部分发生在中美洲。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Anna 1961 track.png}}
飓风安娜很可能源自非洲上空的[[东风波|东风波]]。1961年7月16日，{{link-en|电视红外观测卫星|Television Infrared Observation Satellite}}图像显示[[佛得角|佛得角群岛]]最南面的西南偏西方向约1640公里海域上空有云块存在<ref name="fritz">{{cite journal | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304054231/http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/mwr/090/mwr-090-12-0507.pdf | deadurl = no | url = http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/mwr/090/mwr-090-12-0507.pdf | title = Satellite Pictures And The Origin Of Hurricane Anna | first = Sigmund | last = Fritz | volume = 90 | doi = 10.1175/1520-0493(1962)090<0507:SPATOO>2.0.CO;2 | date = 1962-12 | journal = Monthly Weather Review | publisher = American Meteorological Society, PDF document hosted by National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2016-04-10 | location = [[华盛顿哥伦比亚特区|Washington, D.C.]] | page = 507–513 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。不过，[[美国海军|美国海军]]的侦察机和船只观测报告直到次日才确认这股东风波的存在，系统此时已行进至[[安地卡岛|安地卡岛]]以东约715公里洋面。东风波逼近向风群岛时虽然还缺乏[[大气环流|环流]]，但其内部已经有相当份量的深层[[对流|对流]]，所处位置还在[[热带辐合带|热带辐合带]]附近。7月20日清晨，多艘船只的报告表明[[格林纳达|格林纳达]]和[[特立尼达岛|特立尼达岛]]之间有环流正在发展，<ref name="sju01">{{cite report | title = Report on Hurricane Anna – July 20, 1961 | first = Ralph L. | last = Higgs | date = 1961-08-04 | publisher = San Juan Weather Bureau Office, as archived by the National Hurricane Center | page = 1 | accessdate = 2016-04-10 | location = San Juan, Puerto Rico | type = Report | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304141035/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1961/anna/preloc/pshsju01.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1961/anna/preloc/pshsju01.gif | format = [[GIF|GIF]] }}</ref>格林纳达还出现时速80公里的强烈阵风<ref name="mwr">{{cite report | format = PDF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303201458/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1961.pdf | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1961.pdf | title = The Hurricane Season of 1961 | first = Gordon E. 2 | last = Dunn | date = 1962-03 | publisher = American Meteorological Society, PDF document hosted by National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | journal = Monthly Weather Review | accessdate = 2016-04-10 | volume = 90 | pages = 108, 110 | location = [[迈阿密|Miami]], [[佛罗里达州|Florida]] | doi = 10.1175/1520-0493(1962)090<0107:THSO>2.0.CO;2 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。据[[北大西洋飓风数据库|北大西洋飓风数据库]]记载，经侦察机确认<ref name="mwr" />，系统于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]7月20日凌晨0点发展成热带风暴，因此获名“安娜”（{{lang|en|Anna}}）<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite report | author = National Hurricane Center | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-021716.txt | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2016-02-17 | accessdate = 2016-04-10 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-04-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160410132821/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-021716.txt | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] }}</ref>。

行进至[[多巴哥|多巴哥]]东北偏北方向约40公里海域时，风速约为每小时65公里的安娜马上开始强化，前进方向为正西略偏北面<ref name="HURDAT" />。气象机构于{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}7月20日13点30分发布针对安娜的首份公告，称风暴的持续风速为每小时95公里。当天下午，侦察机在气旋内测得飓风强度几力，安娜因此升级成飓风。<ref name="sju01" />风暴接下来以更趋稳定的速度增强，于7月21日清晨达到二级飓风标准，再于{{lang|en|UTC}}18点强化成三级飓风，成为本季首场大型飓风。{{lang|en|UTC}}7月22日中午12点，气旋达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]185公里，最低[[气压|气压]]976[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，28.8[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）的最高强度。7月23日清晨，安娜的强度回落到二级飓风标准，并开始掠过洪都拉斯北部海岸。飓风继续减弱，到7月24日清晨已弱化成一级飓风。{{lang|en|UTC}}中午12点左右，安娜以风力时速130公里强度从英属洪都拉斯[[斯坦克里克区|斯坦克里克区]]乡下[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]。当天晚上，气旋降级成热带风暴，并在不久后消散。<ref name="HURDAT" />

== 防灾措施 ==
[[美国国家气象局|美国国家气象局]]向[[委内瑞拉|委内瑞拉]]、[[库拉索|库拉索]]、[[博奈尔|博奈尔]]的[[阿鲁巴|阿鲁巴]]发布[[热带气旋警告|热带气旋警告]]<ref name="nhca">{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1961/anna/preloc/pshsju02.gif | title = Report on Hurricane Anna - July 20, 1961 | author = Ralph L. Higgs | date = 1961-08-04 | work = U.S. Weather Bureau Office San Juan, Puerto Rico | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration; National Hurricane Center | deadurl = no | pages = 2 | accessdate = 2016-04-10 | location = San Juan, Puerto Rico | format = GIF | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304034330/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1961/anna/preloc/pshsju02.gif }}</ref>。[[牙买加|牙买加]]的多名气象专家预计风暴会从该岛以南经过，不会对当地造成影响<ref name="tg">{{cite news | newspaper = The Daily Gleaner | date = 1961-07 | title = Anna Should Miss Jamaica}}</ref>。随着安娜继续西进，气象机构预计气旋会从[[尼加拉瓜|尼加拉瓜]]北部或洪都拉斯东南部登陆，建议当地居民及时采取预防措施<ref>{{cite news | agency = [[合众国际社|United Press International]] | date = 1961-07 | title = Hurricane's Sight Set on North Coast of Nicaragua | newspaper = The Daily Courier}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | date = 1961-07 | title = Hurricane Roars Across Caribbean | newspaper = Arizona Daily Sun}}</ref>。[[洪都拉斯湾|洪都拉斯湾]]沿线居民接获警报，注意狂风和可能高达3米的潮汐<ref>{{cite news | title = Anna Bites At British Honduras | date = 1961-07-23 | newspaper = The Miami News}}</ref>。风暴逼近洪都拉斯后，气象部门建议小型船只及其它小艇留在港口内，不要出海<ref>{{cite news | agency = United Press International | date = 1961-07 | title = Hurricanes Path Leading to Honduras | newspaper = Sunday Gazette-Mail}}</ref>。此外，[[天鹅群岛|天鹅群岛]]也接获飓风观察预警<ref>{{cite news | title = Hurricane Aims At Honduras; Warnings Out | date = 1961-07-23 | agency = United Press International | newspaper = The Palm Beach Post | location = Miami, Florida}}</ref>。面对安娜的威胁，英属洪都拉斯有100人被迫离开家园，还有许多商铺关门。[[伯利兹市|伯利兹港]]有许多船只转移到上游内陆水域。<ref name="tdg">{{cite news | newspaper = The Daily Gleaner | date = 1961-07 | title = Anna British Honduras Bound last night}}</ref>气象机构还预测飓风会在英属洪都拉斯山区产生暴雨，引起对当地爆发山洪的担忧<ref name="gbdt">{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | date = 1961-07 | title = Hurricane Anna hits Honduras | newspaper = Great Bend Daily Tribune}}</ref>。此外，英属洪都拉斯的教会福利机构还开始运送衣物及其它应对飓风来袭的物资<ref name="tdg" />。

== 影响 ==
[[File:Tiros_3_and_Hurricane_Anna_(Jul._17,_1961).jpg|thumb]]
安娜在格林纳达产生时速80公里的阵风<ref name="mwr" />。当地受风暴破坏的基本上只有[[香蕉|香蕉]]作物、树木和[[电线杆|电线杆]]<ref name="tg" />。[[巴巴多斯|巴巴多斯]]和[[圣卢西亚|圣卢西亚]]的风力很小，时速仅有47公里<ref name="fritz" />。特立尼达遭受的破坏程度很轻<ref name="sju11" />。委内瑞拉北部和[[ABC群岛|ABC群岛]]多地测得每小时80至113公里风速<ref name="nhca" />，阿鲁巴的一间气象站也测得时速80公里大风<ref name="sju11">{{cite report | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303191125/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1961/anna/preloc/pshsju11.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1961/anna/preloc/pshsju11.gif | title = Report on Hurricane Anna - July 20, 1961 | author = Ralph L. Higgs | date = 1961-08-04 | work = U.S. Weather Bureau Office San Juan, Puerto Rico | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration; National Hurricane Center | page = 11 | accessdate = 2016-04-10 | location = San Juan, Puerto Rico | deadurl = no | format = GIF }}</ref>。

洪都拉斯因安娜遭受中等程度破坏，但破坏范围仅限于大西洋海岸。位于[[特拉|特拉]]的一间气象站在两天内测得7.3到25.4毫米雨量，位于[[科尔特斯港|科尔特斯港]]的另一间气象站则测得50毫米降雨<ref>{{cite report | title = Record Of Observations Made By Honduran Govt. Weather Station Tela, Honduras | work = Tela Railroad Co. | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration; National Hurricane Center | date = 1961-07-27 | accessdate = 2016-04-10 | page = 2 | location = San Juan, Puerto Rico | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1961/anna/preloc/pshmhte2.gif | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303224013/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1961/anna/preloc/pshmhte2.gif | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | format = PDF }}</ref>。该国的普拉普拉亚（{{lang|en|Plaplaya}}）有215户居宅因风暴受损，[[特鲁希略_(洪都拉斯)|特鲁希略]]也有多幢建筑受到破坏<ref name="pshmhtg">{{cite report | title = Report on Hurricane Anna | author = Etat; Gordon E. Dunn | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303174042/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1961/anna/preloc/pshmhtg.gif | date = 1961-08-04 | work = U.S. Weather Bureau Office Miami, Florida | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration; National Hurricane Center | page = 11 | accessdate = 2016-04-10 | location = Miami, Florida | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1961/anna/preloc/pshmhtg.gif | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | format = GIF }}</ref>。[[利蒙_(洪都拉斯)|利蒙]]有9套房屋被毁，另外18套受损严重，无法居住<ref name="pshmhtg" />。[[格拉西亚斯-阿迪奥斯省|格拉西亚斯-阿迪奥斯省]]也受到重创，数以百计的居民因此流离失所<ref name="mgp">{{cite news | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration; National Hurricane Center | date = 1961-07 | title = Miami Gets Pelted With Short Storms | accessdate = 2016-04-10 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | format = GIF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303193805/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1961/anna/news/miami.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1961/anna/news/miami.gif | deadurl = no }}</ref>。[[海湾群岛省|海湾群岛省]]有9套房屋被毁，另外13套受损。[[乌提拉岛|乌提拉岛]]有约5000棵椰树被狂风推倒。<ref name="pshmhtg" />飓风安娜在洪都拉斯一共导致价值30万美元（1961年美元）的破坏<ref name="mwr" />。整场飓风一共导致1人死亡，12人受伤，风暴过后还有许多灾民需要粮食或医疗救助<ref name="mgp" />。气旋在英属洪都拉斯产生阵风和2.1至3米的大浪<ref name="gbdt" />。多份报道称该国也蒙受了相当可观的损失，但具体数额缺乏记载<ref name="mwr" />。

